_aChangeLog.text: Added a line in cells to line Ts up on
Lowered health on a func_breakable secret near disco
Surf winners changed from cage style to platform style
Added a recall button within the playable area of Hide and Seek to prevent CT getting stuck inside
Added scores to Ski-Ball to help CT to understand how the game works
Added a sign above the 2 main portals to better indicate their usage
Improved a few spots in Hide and Seek
Fixed the knife not spawning for Ts to pick up after completing Hide and Seek
Fixed a hollow brush on the sign brush at Ski-Ball
Fixed Ts dying occasionally on Drop Down
Fixed a bug in hide and seek where you would die if you jumped on the seeker box
Fixed vent acting like water leading into armoury
Added a missing "Winners" sign within Descent
Fixed a Z-fighting issue with a door at armoury
Lowered volume of dodge course song from 10 to 7
